I've been watching a lot of Cristine's videos, both old and new, and I've come to the conclusion that Cristine has only gotten prettier with age.  Some of this may be due to her getting better with makeup, but not all of it.  She's always had a killer figure, but she has gotten a little slimmer over the years, which really brings out the bone structure on her face.  Her nose has also gotten a little bolder, which is really becoming for her.  It reminds me of how PewDiePie got better and better looking as he matured.  Just felt like complimenting Cristine, because I think she's lovely.
